  "html": "<p class=\"\">I spearheaded an internal effort to develop <a href=\"https://www.newscaststudio.com/2018/11/05/nbc-big-board-update/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\" data-preview-url=\"https://www.newscaststudio.com/2018/11/05/nbc-big-board-update/\">new D3-powered mapping software</a> for visualizing election maps and results live - the touchscreen app wielded by Steve Kornacki known as the \"Big Board\". Built for real-time county-level election analysis.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The Big Board UI: 2016 Pennsylvania presidential results beside an interactive county map\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1666630396/project-images/nbc_bigboard.png\" alt=\"The Big Board UI: 2016 Pennsylvania presidential results beside an interactive county map\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1666630396/project-images/nbc_bigboard.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1666630396/project-images/nbc_bigboard.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1666630396/project-images/nbc_bigboard.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1666630396/project-images/nbc_bigboard.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The Big Board UI: 2016 Pennsylvania presidential results beside an interactive county map\" width=\"5000\" height=\"2625\" style=\"--splay-rot:-2.63deg;\" data-dimensions=\"5000×2625\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">The Big Board UI: 2016 Pennsylvania presidential results beside an interactive county map</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p4KIMQsVkt8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\" data-preview-url=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p4KIMQsVkt8\">2016 NBC News County-Level Election Maps<svg class=\"inline-block w-4 h-4 ml-1 opacity-50 dark:opacity-75 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity align-text-bottom\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M23.498 6.186a3.02 3.02 0 0 0-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.02 3.02 0 0 0 .502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.02 3.02 0 0 0 2.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.02 3.02 0 0 0 2.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814M9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12z\" class=\"\"></path></svg></a></p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Planning board — printed election-graphic studies and notes pinned to the wall\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1755101296/IMG_5294_dpmmkr.jpg\" alt=\"Planning board — printed election-graphic studies and notes pinned to the wall\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1755101296/IMG_5294_dpmmkr.jpg 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1755101296/IMG_5294_dpmmkr.jpg 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1755101296/IMG_5294_dpmmkr.jpg 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1755101296/IMG_5294_dpmmkr.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Planning board — printed election-graphic studies and notes pinned to the wall\" width=\"3024\" height=\"4032\" style=\"--splay-rot:2.05deg;\" data-dimensions=\"3024×4032\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-[3/4] w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Planning board — printed election-graphic studies and notes pinned to the wall</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Broadcast setup — the Big Board on a control-room monitor beside a waveform scope\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1755101273/IMG_6264_ubgaak.jpg\" alt=\"Broadcast setup — the Big Board on a control-room monitor beside a waveform scope\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1755101273/IMG_6264_ubgaak.jpg 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1755101273/IMG_6264_ubgaak.jpg 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1755101273/IMG_6264_ubgaak.jpg 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1755101273/IMG_6264_ubgaak.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Broadcast setup — the Big Board on a control-room monitor beside a waveform scope\" width=\"4032\" height=\"3024\" style=\"--splay-rot:2.95deg;\" data-dimensions=\"4032×3024\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Broadcast setup — the Big Board on a control-room monitor beside a waveform scope</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Printed design studies for the on-air election graphics, spread across a desk\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1755101285/IMG_5444_mn2u7z.jpg\" alt=\"Printed design studies for the on-air election graphics, spread across a desk\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/